import gemstop from "../assets/Images/GemStop.png";
import osrs from "../assets/Images/osrs.png";
import admin from "../assets/Images/admin.png";

export const Work = [
    {
        id:1,
        name:"GemStops E-Commerce App",
        description:"Responsive application implemented with MERN stack. View products, user authentication and registration, add to shopping cart, and submit an order (credit card or PayPal)",
        img_data: gemstop,
        tags:["react","express","redux",],
        demo:"https://github.com/mattballito/GemStops",
        github:"https://github.com/mattballito/GemStops",
        linkText:"Under Repair",
        linkFontSize: "16px"
    },
    {
        id:2,
        name:"Multiplayer MMO Artifical Intelligence",
        description:"A task automation designed for multiplayer OSRS servers. Built with the RuneMate API, the AI provides robust state validation via a decision tree.",
        img_data: osrs,
        tags:["Java","Kotlin"],
        demo:"https://youtu.be/1eOtTFel8lg",
        github:"https://github.com/mattballito/RuneMateBots",
        linkText: "Visit",
        linkFontSize: "36px"
        
    },
    {
        id:3,
        name:"GemStops Administrator Portal",
        description:"A CRUD interface designed for the GemStops App. The user may update inventory and create products. Analytics, sales data, and web orders may be managed.",
        img_data: admin,
        tags:["react","express","redux"],
        demo:"https://github.com/mattballito/GemStops/tree/main/MERN/dashboard",
        github:"https://github.com/mattballito/GemStops",
        linkText:"Under Repair",
        linkFontSize: "16px"
    },
    /*
    {
        
        id:4,
        name:"Sidebar Menu",
        description:"A cool looking sidebar menu build using ReactJS and styledComponents.It has really smooth animations.",
        img_data: display,
        tags:["react","styledComponents","react-router"],
        
        demo:"https://react-sidebar.vercel.app/",
        github:"https://github.com/codebucks27/react-sidebar"
       
    },{
        id:5,
        name:"Todo App(React + Redux)",
        description:"A todo app build using Redux-toolkit and framer-motion for smooth animations.",
        img_data: display,
        tags:["react","redux","framer-motion"],
        
        demo:"http://react-redux-todo-app-git-main-codebucks27.vercel.app/",
        github:"https://github.com/codebucks27/React-Redux-Todo-App"
        
    },
    {
        id:6,
        name:"Responsive Navigation Menu",
        description:"A reponsive navbar menu component in ReactJS with react-router functionalities. Built from scratch.",

        tags:["react","react-router","css"],
        
        demo:"http://react-responsive-navbar-codebucks27.vercel.app/",
        github:"https://github.com/codebucks27/React-responsive-navbar"
